      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. the swelling is pretty bad though, like it's shaped like a balloon. and i can't really put any weight on it at all, it's like it just won't hold me up. is that normal for a sprain? i'm just worried it might be something worse but i'm trying to avoid the hospital if im not dying lol",
