      "content": "thanks for the reassurance. i'm just a bit nervous because the bone itself feels kinda tender if i touch it, and i heard sometimes if you can't walk on it you might need an xray for a fracture. do you think it's worth the wait for a couple days to see if RICE works first, or should i just stick to what you said and wait it out?",
